Preconditions:
- The input array `nums` must not be null.
- The length of the input array `nums` must be at least 3.
- The elements of the input array `nums` must be integers.
- The elements of the input array `nums` must be between 1 and 10^6 (inclusive).

Postconditions:
- The method returns a long value representing the maximum value over all triplets of indices.
- If all triplets of indices have a negative value, the method returns 0.